main event: An observer in Alexandria reported seeing a bright shining disc-shaped object in the sky on 15 April 1966.
interesting points: The object was larger and brighter than the moon,It remained stationary for several minutes before changing shapes,The observer noted that there was no noise or trail from the object,The sighting lasted approximately 30 minutes,The observer had a background in military intelligence and had typed similar reports in the past.
witness description: A civilian with a military intelligence background.
